You can use generators to make cooperative multitasking inside one thread. I can&#x27;d do that with arrays.<p>Generators aren&#x27;t a data structure - or if they are, then functions are a data structure too. This isn&#x27;t array, this is function:<p><pre><code>    function doStuff() {
      return [
        fs.readFile.bind(null, &#x27;hello.txt&#x27;),
        fs.readFile.bind(null, &#x27;world.txt&#x27;),
        fs.readFile.bind(null, &#x27;and-such.txt&#x27;)
      ];
    }</code></pre>
